# Jottr plugin manifest for the bundled Note Encryptor.
# See syntax.plugg for the full grammar.

=meta=
id      encrypt_decrypt
name    Note Encryptor
version 1.0.0
author  Jottr
icon    lock
description
Encrypt individual note files with a password. Stash encrypted
notes on USB sticks or cloud storage without exposing your text.
Uses XOR + base64 so it has zero external dependencies.

=runtime=
module plugins.encrypt_decrypt
icon   lock

=features=
feature encrypt_note - Encrypt a single note with a password.
feature decrypt_note - Decrypt a single note (password required).
feature encrypt_all   - Bulk-encrypt every note via a file picker.

=hooks=
hook context_menu_file   - Add Encrypt/Decrypt to the file context menu.
hook context_menu_folder - Add Encrypt all/Decrypt all to the folder menu.

=tags=
security, encryption, privacy
